As planning for THE Greatest Homecoming on Earth progresses, please note new #NCAT safety protocols, cancellations and modifications for all associated outdoor and indoor events. ⬆️⁠ *Full details via link in their bio*

. 
. The parade, Aggie Fan Fest, and the annual Student Activities-sponsored Greek cookout have been cancelled.
.

. Additional and full details available via link in their bio.
